Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有这样的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同玩笑一般不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么才能长得像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样吗  像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道她被妈妈给灌输了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这事是绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃…比吕美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是白痴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来不就是打算放弃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了  上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我没有食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有食欲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在烦恼着的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你一起想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过  如果我在身边你就会混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为那是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混乱的原因反而是因为你孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在黑暗里  只要有人相伴左右的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里一定能够坚强起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能找到最终的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会成为真一郎的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  说出来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把这个还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面  今天给你份意外的惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的吧  地面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天中午也不打算吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你便当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别剩下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山芋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个炸鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山芋还没有咽下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向真一郎道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎没有望向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他的视线却避开了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观察你之后就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是绝对不可能飞翔的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让能够飞翔的真一郎为不能飞翔的你而烦恼太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样  太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为是地说了这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你告诉我  我怎么就不明白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你充满了谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连和纯之间的事也没有告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉我  我就和你绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我们就不是什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}还说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那边是不是打架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}所以说你不能飞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖  女生之间打架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}别这样  别这样啦  比吕美冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}比吕美  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这下麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们两个都不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我不明白的话  那希望你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  不就没法一起思考了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就没法帮上真一郎的忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想知道  真一郎的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到真一郎在烦恼  我真的很难过  痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却说我什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她  她该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会…你…喜欢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为只有你才能继承雷轰丸的遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那种喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪种喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  比如交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种恋爱方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美喜欢乃绘的老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是比吕美和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有模有样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他终于有干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都表扬你的舞蹈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  上次要你让我量了一下毛衣的肩宽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我织毛衣织得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  真一郎的毛衣也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女人  是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要和乃绘交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱  麻烦你先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和比吕美交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和乃绘交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有做过那样的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你提出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能遵守承诺的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和比吕美分手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要自以为是到什么地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  你必须遵守承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往…  真一郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  真一郎喜欢的应该不是那个叫乃绘的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（现在可以去你那边吧  三代吉）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚特别的冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冷的地方眉来眼去  也别有情调的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  那件毛衣怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快点穿上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友亲手编织的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为这一辈子都无缘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是  不能帮你织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了  小爱手很笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这种地方正是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对我那么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有资格享受三代吉你的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从真一郎那里听说  三代吉你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前  其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回到店里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  话还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你那下文  不知为何不想去听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是手牵手地回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱你是我的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于昨天的事  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你的事  帮我马上改好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈又硬塞事情给你做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有从你妈妈那里听到些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘的事  让我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老是想着比吕美…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我认为我对乃绘是没有恋爱感情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢的话  也不会这样受她折腾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因为什么交换条件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不是昨天的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像开始恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何  好多地方都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸颊  胸口  耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得不好意思去见真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使改变了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不改变可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一节课是在别馆  冬天真让人冷到受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这样冷  今晚绝对会下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能熬到今晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打赌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪也在下了  今天吃乌冬面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  昨天不也是吃的这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那吃拉面怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}拉面好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那决定咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代吉  饭吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  我不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不  早饭吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀  那算了  找别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  如果是你的话  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…还是让医生去检查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  今天没有带便当来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没有  没有  没…没…有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你等一下吧  等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了的话你又会跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  还是想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么「因为」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你为什么逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么要追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话  快说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的话  我没必要站住  说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限你三秒以内说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…和…我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往？  什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是恋爱那方面的喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经找不到合适的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头不够  明明还需要两个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  会弄脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(650,200)}我喜欢乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在好想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢  明明不伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却特别地  特别地想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她  真的喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这雪要积起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真的会感冒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  上次那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和乃绘交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像连我自己也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也看看我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不可以更加喜欢你？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.12,0:23:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装出一副乖乖女的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻易地俘获男人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有下雪的小镇
